transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Viagra, can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, I currently have a prescription with Score Blue.

Speaker 1: And I've seen advertised Viagra or BGR or something like that.

Speaker 2: Yeah, or AGV, that's the newest pill that we're offering.

Speaker 1: Can I get a sample of that or get prescribed for that?

Speaker 2: Unfortunately, we don't do samples, but you can always put an order in.

Speaker 1: It's going to be 10 pills for 63, it will be in our smallest package.

Speaker 2: Okay, that will be fine. Can you do that?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I can help you with that.

Speaker 2: What is your last name and a zip code so I can pull up your profile here?

Speaker 1: I'm sorry?

Speaker 2: Your last name and a zip code so I can pull up your profile.

Speaker 1: My last name is Michael, M-I-C-H-A-E-L.

Speaker 2: Zip code is 17201.

Speaker 1: Okay, and just to confirm here, we're going to be using the Visa that ends in 7324?

Speaker 2: That's correct.

Speaker 1: Perfect, one second.

Speaker 2: And did you want to do 25, 50, or 100 milligrams? It would be up to you.

Speaker 1: No, just 25.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I'm sorry.

Speaker 2: No, we actually went through it now. The doctor is going to review the script.

Speaker 1: It's going to be 63.95 for the 25 milligrams, 10 pills,

Speaker 2: and you'll receive this in about three to five business days here.

Speaker 1: Okay, all right. Thank you.

Speaker 2: Of course. Have a good one. Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.
